    "desc": "Make your study abroad dream come true with Edvoy. We help you with choosing the right courses from about 38,000+ courses, 120+ universities across 24 countries. Our study abroad consultants guide you further with exams, application processes, visas and more. All this at no cost. We keep students at the heart of everything we do. Chat with us today!",
    "navbar": "Courses\nInstitutions\nAbout",
    "text": "en-edvoy\nCourses\nInstitutions\nAbout\nSign in\nGet Started\nWhere?\nSelect Study Destination\nWhich?\nSelect Course Level\nWhat?\nHow it works\nFind courses\nBrowse the top courses from over 120 universities worldwide\nApply and receive offers\nInstantly apply, upload academic documents and receive offers\nChat with us\nChat with us to receive free expert advise from our friendly advisors\nWe'll help you find the right courses\nSearch from over 38141 courses by subject or university\nSee all popular subjects\nComputer Sciences\nArtificial Intelligence\nBusiness\nCyber Security\nHealth care\nData Sciences and Big Data\nFinance\nEmergency Medicine\nBusiness Administration\nEngineering And Technology\nExplore Top Study Destinations\nWe’re partnered with over 120 world class education providers in 24 countries\nPrevious\nStudy in Canada\nStudy in Ireland\nStudy in New Zealand\nNext\nDiscover Top Universities\nWe’re partnered with over 120 world class education providers\nPrevious\nUniversity of Brighton\nUnited Kingdom\nUniversity of Roehampton\nUnited Kingdom\nCoventry University\nUnited Kingdom\nNext\nStudents at the heart of everything we do\nStudentsPartners\nPrevious\n“Edvoy made it so easy for me, in every step they helped me in understanding”\nJyotisman\nMsc Digital marketing, UWE Bristol\nNext\nFooter\nen-edvoy\nEXPLORE\nCourses\nInstitutions\nDownload App\nNew\nRefer & Earn\nNew\nCourse Finder\nABOUT\nAbout Edvoy\nFor Partners\nPrivacy Policy\nTerms of Service\nCareers\nContact Us\nRESOURCES\nArticles\nKnowledge Base\nEvents\n£\nGBP\nFacebook\nTwitter\nLinkedIn\nInstagram\n© 2020 - 2022 Edvoy™ Educational Services Ltd. All rights reserved.\nStudy Abroad Consultant in Chennai\n|\nStudy Abroad Consultant in Vijayawada\n|\nStudy Abroad Consultant in New Delhi\n|\nStudy Abroad Consultant in Hyderabad",
